{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2382293, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 454880, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "有必要！！！！！！亲身体验，安利支付宝好医保长期医疗，cz这次理赔特别方便，两万多很快到账了。学校公费医疗超级大坑（只能看小病小灾）", "timestamp": 1630217119, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2382339, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 454880, "reply_to": 2382293, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice:  感谢alice的建议，我这就去看看", "timestamp": 1630217381, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2382550, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 454880, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "可是我这次生病花了3w8，学校报了3w2……", "timestamp": 1630219072, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2382600, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 454880, "reply_to": 2382550, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob:  能冒昧问问b君是什么类型的疾病吗", "timestamp": 1630219494, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2382629, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 454880, "reply_to": 2382600, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 先心病，除了材料费基本全cover了", "timestamp": 1630219624, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2382630, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 454880, "reply_to": 2382550, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 医保目录内的才报销", "timestamp": 1630219630, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2382634, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 454880, "reply_to": 2382629, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 心脏手术确实", "timestamp": 1630219645, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2382662, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 454880, "reply_to": 2382293, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 第一，公费医疗只能在学校以及定点医院，如果你寒暑假生病或者你不在学校定点医院做手术，你就一分钱都报不了（cz跟校医院argue了很久）。第二，公费医疗是有比例的，商保可以补足，100%报销。（但是注意支付宝有6年累计10000元的免赔额。）", "timestamp": 1630219791, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2382677, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 454880, "reply_to": 2382293, "tag": null, "text": "cz是腿摔伤了，副韧带损伤。可以在北京做，但是定点的北医三院根本排不上。所以选择回家做，父母照顾也更方便。这样学校是一分也不会报的", "timestamp": 1630219885, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2382696, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 454880, "reply_to": 2382293, "tag": null, "text": "而且寒暑假即使是急诊，报销比例也很低，而且手续非常之复杂。我们年轻长期医疗每个月保费就十块多。我当时订了之后就忘了，没想到这次有用", "timestamp": 1630219971, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2383185, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 454880, "reply_to": 2382696, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 和寒暑假没关系吧，Bob寒暑假在三院医药费也基本全报啊……", "timestamp": 1630222912, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2383253, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 454880, "reply_to": 2383185, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 转诊单啥时候开的？研究生？", "timestamp": 1630223395, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2383398, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 454880, "reply_to": 2383253, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 本科和博士都能啊？转诊单也可以补开啊？只有本科毕业到博士入学那个没学籍的暑假不行。", "timestamp": 1630224190, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 12, "pid": 454880, "reply": 13, "tag": null, "text": "在校生有必要另外买医疗保险吗？\n", "timestamp": 1630216732, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1630224190, "url": "", "vote": {}}}